How to build unit tests for Azure Data Factory?

Leverage Azure DevOps and pytest for Data Factory unit testing

Azure Devops:
Azure DevOps is the tool to continuously build, test, and deploy your code to any platform and cloud. 

Service Connection:
A Service connection is needed to access the resources in the resource group from Azure DevOps. 

1. Create Azure Resource Group
2. Create Azure DevOps Project
3. 1.3 Create Service connection
    Go to project settings, service connection and then select Azure Resource Manager, see also picture below.
